docs {
  Fetches huddles that are currently in progress (SCHEDULED status, today's date, current time within start/end).
  
  **Response:** `ApiResponse<List<HuddleOngoingResponseDTO>>`.
  
  PENDING
  PREVIOUS
  ONGOING
  SCHEDULED
}
